Description:
INDULGE YOUR SENSES
(Land Approx ½ Acre)
Contemporary and classy this five bedroom plus study home leads the way in opulent living. Soaring two storey bay windows, lustrous Brush Box floors and Italian porcelain tiles feature throughout for a truly stunning finish. Striking formal lounge and dining area with impressive bay window. Superbly outfitted the granite kitchen adjoins the spacious meals and family area overlooking the entertaining patio and sparkling in-ground pool. There is also a fully equipped home theatre, extensive mezzanine lounge and large downstairs study with individual access. Impressive accommodation includes five bedrooms, master with WIR and luxurious ensuite with double shower and deep spa bath, second with WIR and ensuite, the third and fourth share the lavish main bathroom, while the fifth bedroom downstairs has the ground floor bathroom to itself. There is also, great storage throughout, separate laundry, triple garage, ducted heating, video intercom, ducted vacuum, alarm system and electronic gates into the circular drive. Close to renowned schools, transport, sporting facilities, Taylors Creek and Keilor Village shops and cafes.
Agents: Nelson Alexander Pty. Ltd.

Description:
Step Into The Light
Generous living zones define this radiant three bedroom home situated in a family-friendly locale within easy reach of a great range of amenities. Spacious step-down living areas include a well-equipped kitchen with modern appliances, dining domain, a huge lounge and spacious family room. The lounge and family room access a paved patio and there is also a rear garden complete with watering system and a relaxing, paved and shaded area. Two of three bedrooms host BIRs and there is a neat bathroom plus ducted heating and cooling, a garden shed, gated side driveway and double garage. The local bus runs right past the front door; playgrounds and parks are a stroll away. Short drive to freeway, shopping centres and schools.

A fantastic home with a spacious interior extending over four levels, with amazing views over picturesque Keilor Village and the Valley. The light filled living, dining, study and kitchen area opens onto a sizeable balcony. There is also a huge top floor terrace with ample room for entertaining. Description:
Big Family Spaces In Just The Right Places
Brilliantly presented and with every convenience you could want. This instantly appealing home is the last word in stylish and practical family living. Comprises: 7 good sized bedrooms, master with full ensuite and walk in robe, formal lounge and dining rooms, well appointed blackwood timber kitchen with granite benchtops and splashback, large rumpus room or theatre room. Fully enclosed sun drenched entertaining area, double garage with remote control roller doors and internal and rear access, and a 4 Car Carport. Large balcony surrounds the home. All the above on approx half acre. Features include: ducted heating, open fire place, Fujitsu split system, spa bath, ducted vacuum system, stainless steel appliances.
